bindsym $mod+Shift+e exit</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2013 06:42:32 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1262/exiting-i3-without-mouse-click/?answer=2160#post-id-2160</guid></item><item><title>Answer by tieni for &lt;p&gt;I am a bit baffled by not having been able to find any answer after having extensively searched this.
